comment: [Incidental or immaterial] Crabbe (POR) is in the paint for longer than three seconds.
R-Slash shows Rondo (SAC) gets his hands on the ball and cleanly strips McCollum (POR).

[Observable in enhanced video] Belinelli (SAC) gathers the ball in the air, landing on both feet. He can use either foot to pivot. Stepping back with his left, he establishes his right foot as pivot. He then steps back with his right, but passes before returning his foot to the floor.
Frazier (POR) makes contact to Cousins' (SAC) arm, affecting his shot.
Casspi (SAC) commits a take foul on Crabbe (POR).
Collison (SAC) commits a take foul on McCollum (POR).
Rondo (SAC) commits a take foul on Leonard (POR).

LHH shows Harkless (POR) makes contact with the ball first on tip-back by Gay (SAC), followed by incidental contact to his hand/arm. NOTE: Due to technical difficulties, certain video links may be unavailable at this time. The report will be reposted once available.
